HEADWORD: Pollute
<hw>Pol*lute"</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>pollutus</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Polluted.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
